{"tid":831694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"坐高鐵赴京述職？　林鄭：行程緊湊　未必合公幹用","createTime":"2018-09-22T07:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T14:23:48.000Z","uid":39464,"like":49,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"bced77719db6397f292628f93093b2279d65aac6","tid":831694,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180922/s00001/ffa6197ff458606a3440b3948801eb0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180922%2Fs00001%2Fffa6197ff458606a3440b3948801eb0d.jpg&h=79004cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣深港高鐵香港段今早在西九龍站舉行開通儀式，特首林鄭月娥及一眾嘉賓在儀式後，一同乘坐高鐵「動感號」列車，出發前往廣州南站。林太見傳媒時被問及，日後上京述職會否乘搭高鐵。她表示，由西九龍站到北京的車程，需要接近9小時，若有充裕時間的話，很願意乘高鐵，「不過恐怕我每一次行程都非常緊湊，長途暫時來說，未必適合我公幹之用」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指出，今午花了43分鐘由西九龍總站不停站前往廣州南站，回程時則曾停留福田站讓部分賓客下車，需時48分鐘，相信許多賓客已在社交媒體分享其經歷。<br />\n<br />\n記者再追問林鄭月娥，她既表明公幹時不坐高鐵，如何吸引市民乘搭。林太回應指，期望傳媒可以像廣大市民般，以正面樂觀的心情迎合高鐵開通，「所以你執住我一句話我公務不會坐，便認為（高鐵）不夠吸引力，便可能不是這種態度」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥自言，每天的睡覺時間只比2至3小時多一點，「在平衡了需要盡量在公務中做更多事，9個小時用在交通上，可能未必是我今日這種情況的考慮」。但對於路程約3至4小時的城市，她認為高鐵是很好的選擇，或比乘搭飛機更可靠。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180922/s00001/1537597750321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180922%2Fs00001%2F1537597750321&d=v8KQLTnareU90bbLtfNQZMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=c697f8f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180922%2Fs00001%2F1537597750321&h=acb02549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180922/s00001/1537597750321</a>"},{"pid":"9e2278bf1cd65c091d8f5e47dff9ca833d9c0dac","tid":831694,"uid":106482,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:30:07.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】全國人大代表譚志源相信，市民對一地兩檢的顧慮會隨着高鐵開通而逐步消除，又稱明年會乘坐高鐵到北京出席兩會會議。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大代表譚志源：「我們和一眾港區人大已經開始討論明年三月上北京開會，是希望在香港乘高鐵上去，屆時看看安排怎樣，就算他們未必如此，我自己亦會乘高鐵上去。以往我做局長時在內地城市之間，我一定在有選擇情況下乘高鐵，因為十分準時，我的行程很緊密。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2ebce0230f72b0dc021471c73323c58836dd64","tid":831694,"uid":23786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:31:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f63fb7b2b733c37144fe04a4302f864801248f0","tid":831694,"uid":25771,"like":1,"dislike":29,"score":-28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:33:04.000Z","msg":"有乜問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc53f1437b8e866b5d9134e24eecda3997d0ee08","tid":831694,"uid":198165,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:34:02.000Z","msg":"高鐵做物流就得<br />\n長途？收皮啦"},{"pid":"faf9a41521381908f8e7d97148ef2db61429fb41","tid":831694,"uid":19004,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:41:59.000Z","msg":"賣抽車比順豐做長途快速送貨仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c6a016f6775dc5f22152bbabe87639735ba5c9","tid":831694,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc53f1437b8e866b5d9134e24eecda3997d0ee08","tid":831694,"uid":198165,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:34:02.000Z","msg":"高鐵做物流就得<br />\n長途？收皮啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:43:43.000Z","msg":"物流？好似大少少既行李都唔俾帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98dfd867ad439c53f805